Title: On the finiteness of noncommutative supersymmetric QED$_3$ in the  covariant superfield formulation
Authors: A. F. Ferrari and H. O. Girotti and M. Gomes and A. A. Ribeiro and A. Yu. Petrov and A. J. da Silva
Abstract: The three-dimensional noncommutative supersymmetric QED is investigated within the superfield approach. We prove the absence of UV/IR mixing in the theory at any loop order and demonstrate its one-loop finiteness.
